nal arena. Through his study of Attwood's career and the development of his philosophy, David Moss reveals the impact of industrialism on the individual and society.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 7aBIOGRAPHY & AUTOBIOGRAPHY / Political.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978077356208040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780773562080423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780773562080/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles